{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Mac 1.0","content":"<div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"font-family:Verdana, sans-serif;clear:both;text-align:justify;\">\n<p><a href=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2014/03/apple-macintosh-1984.jpg\"><img data-attachment-id=\"668\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2014/03/21/mac-1-0/apple-macintosh-1984/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2014/03/apple-macintosh-1984.jpg?w=512&#038;h=344\" data-orig-size=\"512,344\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;TheNovo&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1395359663&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Apple Macintosh 1984\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2014/03/apple-macintosh-1984.jpg?w=512&#038;h=344?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2014/03/apple-macintosh-1984.jpg?w=512&#038;h=344?w=512\" class=\"size-full wp-image-668\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2014/03/apple-macintosh-1984.jpg?w=512&#038;h=344\" alt=\"Apple Macintosh OS  - 1984 \" width=\"512\" height=\"344\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2014/03/apple-macintosh-1984.jpg 512w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2014/03/apple-macintosh-1984.jpg?w=150&amp;h=101 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2014/03/apple-macintosh-1984.jpg?w=450&amp;h=302 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\" /></a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"font-family:Verdana, sans-serif;clear:both;text-align:justify;\"></div>\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"font-family:Verdana, sans-serif;clear:both;text-align:justify;\">It was created in 1984. I got it yesterday. It&#8217;s brilliant! The first ever GUI based OS! It&#8217;s pure genius! I got an emulator online users to run the first ever version of the Macintosh OS.</div>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><!--more--><br />\n<span style=\"font-family:Verdana, sans-serif;\">And here&#8217;s the amazing thing: it has all the basic features of our modern day OS. It&#8217;s black and white, lacks networking, and I am facing a problem to link it to my hardware (printers and stuff). However, I downloaded a few vintage games. As it turns out, in those days *.dsk files would run on the Mac. These &#8216;disk&#8217; files stored a collection of softwares. Even in those days, the games were pretty advanced. The refresh rate was much lower, but that&#8217;s obvious.</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family:Verdana, sans-serif;\">Here&#8217;s something I found interesting. A few of my friends and myself included have made a few simple games in Java (although they made games that were much more advanced than mine). Even though I tried to eliminate the screen from flickering using a buffer technique my friend had suggested, the fps wasn&#8217;t enough. In those days, these problems were faced! ðŸ˜€ I was playing the classic brick breaking game, and there I saw the flash.</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family:Verdana, sans-serif;\">It was really amazing to see the OS work. It even had a basic version of Windows Paint (the original mac version from which Windows got the idea, of course). All in all, I&#8217;m pretty excited to be using an OS from 1984.</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family:Verdana, sans-serif;\"><br />\n</span>Here&#8217;s a screenshot:</p>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_668\" style=\"width: 512px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2014/03/apple-macintosh-1984.jpg\"><img data-attachment-id=\"668\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2014/03/21/mac-1-0/apple-macintosh-1984/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2014/03/apple-macintosh-1984.jpg?w=512&#038;h=344\" data-orig-size=\"512,344\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;TheNovo&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1395359663&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Apple Macintosh 1984\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2014/03/apple-macintosh-1984.jpg?w=512&#038;h=344?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2014/03/apple-macintosh-1984.jpg?w=512&#038;h=344?w=512\" class=\"size-full wp-image-668\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2014/03/apple-macintosh-1984.jpg?w=512&#038;h=344\" alt=\"Apple Macintosh OS  - 1984 \" width=\"512\" height=\"344\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2014/03/apple-macintosh-1984.jpg 512w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2014/03/apple-macintosh-1984.jpg?w=150&amp;h=101 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2014/03/apple-macintosh-1984.jpg?w=450&amp;h=302 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\" /></a><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Apple Macintosh OS<br />&#8211; 1984</figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n","date":"2014-03-21T05:06:00.000Z","slug":"mac-1-0","excerpt":"<p>It was created in 1984. I got it yesterday. It&#8217;s brilliant! The first ever GUI based OS! It&#8217;s pure genius! I got an emulator online users to run the first ever version of the Macintosh OS.</p>\n","jetpack_featured_media_url":""},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Nabhoneel's Parchments","subtitle":"All thing photographed and written down"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"fab2273f-880b-523b-83e5-af28122c4b82"}}